Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 4.19 16/40] cifs: Allocate encryption header through kmalloc
Date:   Wed, 15 Apr 2020 07:45:59 -0400
Message-Id: <20200415114623.14972-16-sashal@kernel.org>
